# Problem Statement
problem_statement: "Most domain experts under $20K/month struggle to market themselves. NerdDigital gives you the marketing infrastructure of a 7-figure businessâ€”through a simple done-for-you subscription. No hiring required."

# Experts Marquee
experts:
